<p>If you are looking to play high school lacrosse in the state of Indiana and your school does not have a team your best opportunity to play is to start your own team.  
We can help you start you own team.  If you would like help staring your own team please contact Paul Borchelt <a href="mailto:pborchelt@gmail.com"><span class="c8">pborchelt@gmail.com</a> </p>
 
 <p>To learn more about what is involved in starting a lacrosse team please click here: <a href="http://www.uslacrossechapters.org/indiana/AboutUSLacrosse/StartLacrosse.aspx">Indiana USL Chapter</a></p>
 
 <p>If you already have a team and would like to join the IHSLA please <a href="leagueinfo.php?subpage=Join">click here.</a></p>
